('23ca239b-6b61-4288-b98a-5ca9e99afea4','ui_coffee_hero_subtitle','*','{"label":{"tr":"Fincanınızdaki semboller, yapay zekanın vizyonu ve kadim bilgelikle dile geliyor.","en":"The symbols in your cup come to life through the vision of artificial intelligence and ancient wisdom.","de":"Die Symbole in Ihrer Tasse erwachen durch die Vision der künstlichen Intelligenz und uralte Weisheit zum Leben."}}'),
